===Pronunciation===
*[[AHD]]: īs'krēm
*[[IPA]]: /ˈaɪskriːm/
*[[SAMPA]]: /"aIskri:m/

===Etymology===

Originally ''iced cream''.

===Alternative spellings===
*[[ice-cream]]

===Noun===
'''ice cream''' (''[[uncountable]] and [[countable]]''; ''plural'' '''[[ice creams]]''')

#(''uncountable'') A [[dessert]] made from [[frozen]] [[sweeten]]ed [[cream]] or a similar substance, usually [[flavor]]ed.
#(''countable'') A snack consisting of ice cream (1) in a wafer cone.

====Synonyms====
*(''dessert'') [[iced cream]] (''dated'')
*(''in a wafer cone''): [[cone]], [[cornet]], [[ice cream cone]]

